{"type": "article", "id": 21415, "title": "液体计重器", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-28T07:32:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 96, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702105457YkKcLf9TXivIlFZr.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款液体计重器，来自美国设计师 James Stumpf。它是用玻璃做的，围绕着上半边缘是一圈数字，当人站上去后，压力会推着管内的液体到相应的刻度上，非常有趣。不过它的称量方式难免有一些误差，它具有更多的娱乐性。这款计重器还是一个概念，<a href=\"http://stumpfstudio.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150941wcEa8kGJsCXMSI1R.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"421\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261509424o2YVz1ShDdGpOu5.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150942rYPHgUqQAXMkfcnC.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"676\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150943IWlin7rmLDFzhVkt.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"401\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61692308\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}